description: Retrieves one or more code coverage reports.

parameters.name: reportArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the report for which test cases are returned.

parameters.name: sortBy
parameters.description: Specifies how the results are sorted. Possible values are: FILE_PATH The results are sorted by file path. LINE_COVERAGE_PERCENTAGE The results are sorted by the percentage of lines that are covered.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If there are more items to return, this contains a token that is passed to a subsequent call to DescribeCodeCoverages to retrieve the next set of items.

nested_items.name: codeCoverages
nested_items.description: An array of CodeCoverage objects that contain the results.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The identifier of the code coverage report.

nested_items.name: filePath
nested_items.description: The path of the test report file.

nested_items.name: lineCoveragePercentage
nested_items.description: The percentage of lines that are covered by your tests.

nested_items.name: linesCovered
nested_items.description: The number of lines that are covered by your tests.

nested_items.name: linesMissed
nested_items.description: The number of lines that are not covered by your tests.

nested_items.name: branchCoveragePercentage
nested_items.description: The percentage of branches that are covered by your tests.

nested_items.name: branchesCovered
nested_items.description: The number of conditional branches that are covered by your tests.

nested_items.name: branchesMissed
nested_items.description: The number of conditional branches that are not covered by your tests.

nested_items.name: expired
nested_items.description: The date and time that the tests were run.
